<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1090970-i-had-difficulty-liking-any-of-the-main">I had difficulty liking any of the main characters. Anyone else feel this way?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1090970'><a id="like_count_community_question_1090970" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1090970?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">6 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F331319.An_American_Tragedy">like</a></span>

</li>
