<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/967298-is-this-book-suitable-for-a-text-for-esl">Is this book suitable for a text for ESL students?
I am reading this book and enjoy. I like Dreiser`s writing because of his prose. I am not a native English speaker so that I cannot comprehend his writing as a suitable text used for studying English in an advance class. I will appreciate if anyone offers his or her comments. thanks.</a>
</div>
