<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5522813366158528003">Theodore Herman Albert Dreiser was an American novelist and journalist. He pioneered the naturalist school and is known for portraying characters whose value lies not in their moral code, but in their persistence against all obstacles, and literary situations that more closely resemble studies of nature than tales of choice and agency.<br/><br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theodore_Dreiser'>http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theodore...</a></span>
  <span id="freeText5522813366158528003" style="display:none">Theodore Herman Albert Dreiser was an American novelist and journalist. He pioneered the naturalist school and is known for portraying characters whose value lies not in their moral code, but in their persistence against all obstacles, and literary situations that more closely resemble studies of nature than tales of choice and agency.<br /><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theodore_Dreiser">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theodore...</a></span>
  <a data-text-id="5522813366158528003" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

